{"tid":1569801,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[白宮聯署]支持美國通過《保護香港法 PROTECT Hong Kong Act》，中止出售武器予香港警畜","createTime":"2019-09-14T17:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T15:46:23.000Z","uid":47480,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"31149929fbf0ec08ccfd766f17def4e7fd96343c","tid":1569801,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T17:58:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聯署Link:</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hongkongers-urge-congress-pass-protect-hong-kong-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhongkongers-urge-congress-pass-protect-hong-kong-act&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=9db44f22\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hongkongers-urge-congress-pass-protect-hong-kong-act</a><br />\n<strong>***記得簽完要check E-mail confirm啊***</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法案內容(全文):</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://mcgovern.house.gov/UploadedFiles/HK_PROTECT_Act_FINAL.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmcgovern.house.gov%2FUploadedFiles%2FHK_PROTECT_Act_FINAL.pdf&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=82ab6bc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://mcgovern.house.gov/UploadedFiles/HK_PROTECT_Act_FINAL.pdf</a><br />\n<strong>簡要:</strong><br />\n香港警暴問題備受國際關注，民主黨籍眾議員麥高文（Jim McGovern）周二提出法案，名為《保護香港法》（PROTECT Hong Kong Act），<span style=\"color: red;\">要求禁止美國政府向包括港警在內的紀律部隊，出售人群管制裝備。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190912/large/1568261042_5ce7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190912%2Flarge%2F1568261042_5ce7.jpg&h=cdd6e09f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命，五大訴求，缺一不可。</span>"},{"pid":"f292f9fcab38969c24ec66a3cd86ad963798287f","tid":1569801,"uid":30